{"article_id":"fh3HXXXWovOK99PG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FBI agent Peter Strzok put the Trump-Russia investigation on a fast track during the 2016 election season","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"at the same time","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he was sending text messages to his lover","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"condemning the Republican presidential candidate as an \" idiot \"","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"and vowing to \" stop \" him .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Justice Department Inspector General Michael Horowitz , in a voluminous report , singled out as troubling Mr. Strzok ' s decision","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to move quickly from working on Hillary Clinton ' s email case to investigating Mr. Trump .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"\" In assessing Strzok ' s decision","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"to prioritize the Russia investigation ...","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"these text messages led us to conclude","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"that we did not have confidence","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"that Strzok ' s decision was free from bias , \"","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Mr. Horowitz wrote .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Horowitz ' s 500-plus-page report focused on the Clinton email saga , not Russia .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"A separate inquiry into how the FBI started and conducted the investigation into Russia election interference is continuing .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"because Mr. Strzok ' s texts to former FBI counsel Lisa Page dealt with both ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Mr. Horowitz examined Russia-connected messages .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"He condemned them .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" We were deeply troubled by text messages","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"sent by Strzok and Page","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"that potentially indicated or created the appearance","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"that investigative decisions were impacted by bias or improper considerations , \"","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"the inspector general said .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Mr. Strzok was a pivotal player .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"He was the FBI ' s lead agent in the Clinton probe","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"and then took the same role in Trump-Russia","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"and opted to open a counterintelligence investigation in late July 2016 .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"What followed were a number of controversial decisions ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"such as embracing the Democratic Party-financed , anti-Trump dossier .","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"The FBI also hired the dossier ' s author , former British spy Christoper Steele ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"to continue investigating Mr. Trump after the November election .","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"The FBI then fired Mr. Steele","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"for leaking to news media .","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Strzok ' s role in the Steele narrative will be addressed in Mr. Horowitz ' s next project .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"His Clinton report did not mention the dossier or the FBI ' s use of it","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to acquire surveillance warrants on a Trump campaign volunteer .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Special counsel Robert Mueller fired Mr. Strzok in July 2017","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"after Mr. Horowitz apprised him of the Strzok-Page texts and their affair .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Ms . Page worked on the Mueller team for about six months .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Strzok messaged Ms . Page in May 2017","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that he was reluctant to join the Mueller team","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"because he did not know","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"whether the inquiry would amount to much .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The message would indicate","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that after 10 months of investigating , FBI agents had not found evidence of Trump-Russia collusion .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" I hesitate in part","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"because of my gut sense and concern","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"there ' s no big there there , \"","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Mr. Strzok told his lover .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Horowitz ' s Clinton report took special interest in Mr. Strzok ' s decision","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to fast-track the Trump investigation .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"The inspector general focused on one of Mr. Strzok ' s well-known messages","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"- that \" we can ' t take that risk \" of a Trump election win","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"and that he had an \" insurance policy \" against it .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"The FBI agent ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"who was demoted from counterintelligence to FBI human resources ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"claimed","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"the comment was innocent .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Republicans have wondered","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"whether the \" insurance policy \" statement referred to the unproven dossier or the investigation itself .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Said Mr. Horowitz :","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"\" Strzok said","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"the reference in his text message to an ' insurance policy ' reflected his conclusion","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that the FBI should investigate the allegations thoroughly right away ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"as if Trump were going to win . \"","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"How Mr. Strzok conducted the Trump investigation was influenced by news media indications","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that Mrs. Clinton was sure to win .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The inspector general said :","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"\" As part of this discussion , the team debated how aggressive to be","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and whether to use overt investigative methods .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Given that Clinton was the ' prohibitive favorite '","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"to win ...","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"Strzok said","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"that they discussed","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"whether it made sense to compromise sensitive sources and methods","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"to ' bring things to some sort of precipitative conclusion and understanding . ' \"","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"Mr. Strzok also downplayed his most explosive message","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"- that Mr. Trump would not become president","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"because \" We ' ll stop it . \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"\" When asked about this text message , \"","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"the Horowitz report said ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" Strzok stated","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"that he did not specifically recall sending it ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"but that he believed","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"that it was intended to reassure Page","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"that Trump would not be elected ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"not to suggest","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"that he would do something","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"to impact the investigation .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"Strzok told the OIG","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that he did not take any steps","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"to try to affect the outcome of the presidential election . \"","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Mr. Strzok said","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"if he wanted to affect the outcome ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"then he could have leaked the Russia investigation to news media .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Here are some of Mr. Strzok ' s comments about Mr. Trump :","depth":4},{"id":98,"text":"⦁ March 3 , 2016 :","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"\" God trump is a loathsome human . \"","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"⦁ July 21 , 2016 :","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"\" Trump is a disaster .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"I have no idea","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"how destabilizing his Presidency would be . \"","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"⦁ Aug. 26 , 2016 :","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"\" Just went to a southern Virginia Walmart .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"I could SMELL the Trump support ... \"","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"⦁ Oct. 19 , 2016 :","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"\" I am riled up .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Trump is a f-king idiot ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"is unable to provide a coherent answer . \"","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"⦁ Nov. 7 , 2016 :","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"\" OMG THIS IS F-KING TERRIFYING \"","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"( referencing a New York Times article","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"titled \" A victory by Mr. Trump remains possible \" ) .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"From July to November 2016 , Mr. Strzok ramped up the Trump case","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"by using the dossier","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"to obtain warrants","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"and guide the investigation .","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"Fired FBI Director James B. Comey said in an interview","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"that his job was to see","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"whether agents could replicate the dossier ' s collusion charges ,","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"which remain unconfirmed publicly .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"After hearing Mr. Strzok ' s assurances","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"that he conducted a fair investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Mr. Horowitz wrote :","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"\" When one senior FBI official , Strzok ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"who was helping to lead the Russia investigation at the time ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"conveys in a text message to another senior FBI official , Page ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"' we ' ll stop ' candidate Trump from being elected","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"- after other extensive text messages between the two disparaging candidate Trump -","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"it is not only indicative of a biased state of mind","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"but , even more seriously , implies a willingness","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"to take official action","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"to impact the presidential candidate ' s electoral prospects . \"","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"In March , Attorney General Jeff Sessions named John Huber , U.S. attorney in Utah ,","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"to oversee an investigation into how the FBI used the Steele dossier","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"to obtain warrants on Trump volunteer Carter Page .","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"Mr. Horowitz also is looking at that issue","depth":2},{"id":140,"text":"and whether the Obama administration spied on the Trump campaign for political purposes .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":279,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":255,"right":278,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":237,"right":254,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":164,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":145,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":0,"right":144,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":1,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":2,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":153,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":146,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":150,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"right":149,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":9,"relation":"context","nu